verbose_text: The median level of ADAMTS-4 was 0 ng/mL in the ' normal ' group (with one patient having a detectable amount of 0.3 ng/mL), 0 ng/mL in the injury group (range 0-29.8, with 32 patients having detectable levels), 1.2 ng/mL in the OA samples (range 0-11.5, with six patients having detectable levels) and 1.3 ng/mL in the combined injury and OA group (range 0-15.4, with 21 patients having detectable levels).
